{"tid":1895880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港新型肺炎確診個案累計增至81宗　兩新患者無病徵","createTime":"2020-02-24T20:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T02:13:57.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86eac3258d99eee2b4daa491ed47aa0c8b1e283f","tid":1895880,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"本港新型肺炎確診個案累計增至81宗 兩新患者無病徵<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1510554_1_L_20200224234550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1510554_1_L_20200224234550.jpg&h=2b11d7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞生防護中心指兩名新確診病人都沒有病徵，列為輸入個案。（港台圖片）<br />\n本港新增7宗確診感染新型肺炎的個案，累計個案81宗。衞生防護中心網頁晚上公布，兩名新確診病人都沒有病徵，列為輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n分別一男一女的病人，都是57歲，在瑪麗醫院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n其餘5宗今日新增確診個案，兩人去過北角「福慧精舍」佛堂、兩宗是「鑽石公主號」返港乘客，另一宗是本月初曾返內地的35歲商人。"},{"pid":"93976aa309726ad06c17e2e9880374adaab5607c","tid":1895880,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d7c2ee61f7422abb505fbf70cd5954d55a0da1","tid":1895880,"uid":74368,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:02:14.000Z","msg":"我懷疑有好多人中左<br />\n但自己免疫力夠打低隻病毒"},{"pid":"c36a4e98a8e9916bfcc08b994470dba278dfbdd2","tid":1895880,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:47:15.000Z","msg":"有冇醫汁link"},{"pid":"85bac50b769a6d29d93e47ceae749ab9ec127ffe","tid":1895880,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6d7c2ee61f7422abb505fbf70cd5954d55a0da1","tid":1895880,"uid":74368,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:02:14.000Z","msg":"我懷疑有好多人中左<br />\n但自己免疫力夠打低隻病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"風土病 專殺廢老<img sr